snippet.title: Executive CONFIRMS Amber Heard Petition Did Nothing - They DON'T CARE
snippet.description:
Let's talk about the recent news surrounding Amber Heard and Aquaman 2. A Producer of the film has confirmed they know what fans have said online and they don't care. Let's discuss what needs to be done now. Let me know what you think and make sure to subscribe to the channel for more content!! #Aquaman2 #AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
